492
00:35:43,935 --> 00:35:46,659
I thought you were cheating with him!

493
00:35:46,735 --> 00:35:48,400
With our gay cable guy?

494
00:35:48,435 --> 00:35:53,098
I didn't know he was gay!
I didn't know Justin was either!

495
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:57,313
Now the cops think 
