496
00:35:57,535 --> 00:35:58,600
Well, you sort of are.

497
00:35:58,635 --> 00:36:00,511
You provoked me!

498
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:08,579
You were pretending to have an affair
just to punish me!

499
00:36:09,435 --> 00:36:12,619
Well, obviously!

500
00:36:15,200 --> 00:36:17,841
So now I need you to lie again.

501
00:36:18,535 --> 00:36:22,000
