you <i>were</i> having an affair,

502
00:36:22,035 --> 00:36:25,700
and that I just beat up the wrong guy.

503
00:36:25,735 --> 00:36:27,148
Guys.

504
00:36:27,835 --> 00:36:30,800
I am not lying for you, Carlos.

505
00:36:30,835 --> 00:36:35,800
Gabby, if this charge sticks,
I get sent away for eight years.

506
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,530
Am I supposed to be impressed?

507
00:36:38,035 --> 00:36:43,000
Because of your little stunt with my birth control pills,
I've lost my freedom for the next <i>eighteen</i> years!

508
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:48,078
Gabby, please don't do this.

509
00:36:48,835 --> 00:36:50,300
Gabby!

510
00:36:50,335 --> 00:36:53,443
Don't walk away!

511
00:36:54,735 --> 00:36:55,706
Gabby!

512
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:02,700
